outline of features

1. posts
  - publishing queue
    - posts go in a publishing queue and are published on their publish_on value/column
  - threaded comments
    - cte for retrieving threaded comments
  - post/user admin
    - delete/hide posts
    - ban users
  - tags/categories
  - sort by date/comments/published on
  - "share" post
    - tweet
    - facebook
  - search posts
  - similar posts
  - activity audit log
2. users
  - social network sign in
    - github
    - facebook
    - twitter
3. extendability